hopobject.body: What are the hours of work? bactrim alternatives pcp They are not all 30-minute wonders. A few are special-occasion dinners, and some require minimal preparation but take a full hour or more of unattended cooking in the oven but the bulk are neat little dinners you can have on the table in half an hour or so. We are not chasing perfection here. Just straightforward, delicious cooking. For the times we just want to eat.
